OL,3,CStarmer revives weekly National
OL,4,CSecurity Council meetings
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer as prime minister is
OL,7,Fholding weekly meetings of the
OL,8,FNational Security Council (NSC) for
OL,9,Fthe first time in years.
OL,11,FI have learned that it meets every
OL,12,Fweek after cabinet for a full hour,
OL,13,Fchaired by Starmer, having met more
OL,14,Fsporadically and infrequently when
OL,15,FBoris Johnson and Rishi Sunak were
OL,16,Fprime ministers.
OL,18,FA senior security source said: "Boris
OL,19,FJohnson wasn't keen on having meetings
OL,20,Fand Sunak wasn't desperately
OL,21,Finterested in foreign policy.
