OL,3,CStarmer revives weekly National
OL,4,CSecurity Council meetings
OL,6,F"We've all been recommending Starmer
OL,7,Fshould hold meetings on a much more
OL,8,Fregular basis and put the NSC back at
OL,9,Fthe heart of assessing risk to our
OL,10,Fsecurity and the big foreign policy
OL,11,Fchallenges."
OL,13,FAnother said: "Under Johnson it met
OL,14,Fabout once a month and he would
OL,15,Ffrequently cancel them at short
OL,16,Fnotice. It was frustrating."
OL,18,FThe NSC is now meeting at lunchtime on
OL,19,FTuesdays on a weekly cycle. When it
OL,20,Fwas set up by David Cameron in 2010 it
OL,21,Fmet weekly, in the early afternoon.
