OL,6,FIt was created in response to
OL,7,Fcriticism that under Tony Blair the
OL,8,Fbig foreign policy, defence and
OL,9,Fsecurity decision were taken by Blair
OL,10,Ftoo informally by what was known as
OL,11,F"sofa" government.
OL,13,FA colleague of Cameron recalls how
OL,14,Fimportant the meetings were to him.
